body.name: First Aid Empty Kit, Professional Large Capacity Emergency Response Trauma Bag,Paramedic Multi Pockets Bag, Ideal for Medical First Responder, Rescue, Nurse
features: ▶ Our first aid bags are made of heavy-duty and durable water-resistant nylon material, inner filled with foam,well-constructed. Anti-scratch bottom to reduce the risk of friction for last long use

▶ Super Large capacity: 66*30*28CM, It features 2 side and 2 front zippered pockets for easy access to often-used emergency supplies, the main compartment has 3 dividers attached with velcro on the wall of the bag, great to classify the emergent supplies, In addition, inside with 3 removable pouches, designed for packing small accessories
▶ Bottom of EMT bag with reflective striping for added visibility, easy to find in the dark night

▶ The first responder trauma bag features a wide variety of easy to access compartments that will hold the medical supplies you need. Its main compartment has dividers which make it easy to organize supplies and equipment
▶ Adjustable & removable padded shoulder strap and velcro handle strap convenient to carry
